# REST Client (VS Code) / IntelliJ HTTP Client format.
# Uruchom docker compose up, a potem odpalaj po kolei.

@authUrl = http://localhost:8001
@habitsUrl = http://localhost:8002
@email = marcin@example.com
@password = SuperSecret123

### 1) Rejestracja
POST {{authUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "display_name": "Marcin"
}

### 2) Logowanie — zapisz access_token
# @name login
POST {{authUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 3) /me — info o zalogowanym userze
GET {{authUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### 4) Utwórz nawyk
# @name createHabit
POST {{habitsUrl}}/habits
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bieganie",
  "description": "5 km o poranku",
  "target_per_week": 4
}

### 5) Lista moich nawyków
GET {{habitsUrl}}/habits
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### 6) Zaloguj wykonanie (dzisiaj)
POST {{habitsUrl}}/habits/{{createHabit.response.body.id}}/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "note": "Rano, 6 km"
}

### 7) Historia logów
GET {{habitsUrl}}/habits/{{createHabit.response.body.id}}/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### 8) Statystyki nawyku
GET {{habitsUrl}}/habits/{{createHabit.response.body.id}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### 9) Aktualizuj nawyk
PATCH {{habitsUrl}}/habits/{{createHabit.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target_per_week": 5
}

### 10) Usuń nawyk
DELETE {{habitsUrl}}/habits/{{createHabit.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### --- Negatywne ścieżki (do demonstracji error handlingu) ---

### 11) Rejestracja z krótkim hasłem → 422 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{authUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.pl",
  "password": "123",
  "display_name": "X"
}

### 12) Logowanie złym hasłem → 401 UNAUTHORIZED
POST {{authUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "zleHaslo!!"
}

### 13) Dostęp bez tokenu → 401 UNAUTHORIZED
GET {{habitsUrl}}/habits
